Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Fixes the '0 matches' problem on the Discover tab. Root cause: it was
hitting the main /news endpoint which heavily filters to BOTTLENECK-tier
signals (~47 articles total), so corporate actions never made it through.

NEW SERVER ROUTE: /api/v1/special-situations/feed
  - Fetches 14 RSS feeds DIRECTLY in parallel (8s timeout each):
    IN: ET Markets, ET Industry, Livemint Companies, BS Companies,
        BS Markets, NDTV Profit
    US: MarketWatch Top, MarketWatch Markets, SeekingAlpha News,
        CNBC Top, CNBC Finance
    Global: Reuters Business, Reuters Tech, Yahoo Finance
  - Lightweight regex-based RSS + Atom parser (covers <item> and <entry>)
  - Strips CDATA + inline HTML, decodes XML entities
  - Applies 4 corporate-action classifiers with REJECT patterns to kill
    rumour / negation noise:
      SPIN — spin-off/demerger/carve-out/Form 10/hive-off/breakup
      MA   — open offer/takeover/acquisition/merger/buyout/control change
             rejects: rumoured, in talks, denied, called off, withdrawn
      TURN — back to profit/loss to profit/turnaround/debt restructur
             rejects: failed turnaround, swung to loss, loss widens
      CAP  — buyback/repurchase/special dividend/bonus issue/dividend hike
             rejects: cancelled buyback, dividend cut/suspended
  - Extracts tickers (Indian .NS/.BO suffix + filtered caps tokens)
  - Dedupes by canonical title across sources
  - Sorts latest first within each category
  - Cache 30 min server-side, with ?refresh=1 force-refresh
  - Returns: { last_updated, total, by_category: { SPIN, MA, TURN, CAP },
              source_status: [{ name, ok, items }] }

FRONTEND: Discover tab fully rewritten:
  - Calls the new endpoint (no more /news dependency)
  - Live indicator pill: GREEN ≤30m, AMBER ≤2h, RED older
  - Region filter: ALL / IN / US / GLOBAL (per-item region tagging)
  - Manual 'Refresh now' button forces server-side re-fetch
  - Each match row: region flag, ticker chips, freshness badge (≤24h = 🆕),
    source, title, description preview, external-link icon
  - Source-health panel at bottom shows which RSS feeds pulled successfully
    and how many items each returned (institutional transparency)

Type-check clean.
